CAROLERS DESIGN TOKENS - Quick Reference

=== SPACING SCALE ===
xs: 0.25rem (4px)   - tight spacing
sm: 0.5rem (8px)    - small gaps
md: 1rem (16px)     - standard/default
lg: 1.5rem (24px)   - generous spacing
xl: 2rem (32px)     - spacious
2xl: 3rem (48px)    - hero spacing

Usage: p-lg, gap-md, mb-xs, pt-sm, etc.

=== BORDER RADIUS ===
rounded-lg: 0.5rem (8px)      - input, small elements
rounded-xl: 0.75rem (12px)    - buttons, badges
rounded-2xl: 1rem (16px)      - medium cards
rounded-3xl: 1.5rem (24px)    - large cards
rounded-[2rem]: 2rem (32px)   - hero cards, events

Rules:
- All event cards: rounded-[2rem]
- All vote/song cards: rounded-[1.5rem]
- All buttons: rounded-xl
- All inputs: rounded-lg
- All badges: rounded-full

=== SHADOWS ===
shadow-sm: default - subtle
shadow-md-lift: hover state for cards
shadow-lg-lift: prominent state
shadow-glow: festive accent glow

Rule: Cards hover at shadow-md-lift, never shadow-lg

=== COLORS ===
primary (red):      actions, focus, festive
secondary (green):  supporting, confirmation
accent (gold):      highlights, success
slate:              neutral text, borders, disabled

Border colors:
- Default: border-2 border-slate-200 or border-primary/10
- Hover: border-primary/30
- Active: border-primary/50

=== ANIMATIONS ===
hover: y-4 to y-6, scale-1.01 to scale-1.02 (cards)
shadow: shadow-sm → shadow-md-lift on hover
duration: 300ms transitions

Celebratory:
- animate-pulse-glow: "coming soon" badges
- animate-celebrate: vote celebration effect

=== COMPONENT PATTERNS ===

CARDS:
- border-2 border-primary/10 hover:border-primary/30
- shadow-sm hover:shadow-md-lift
- rounded-[2rem] or rounded-[1.5rem]
- transition-all duration-300
- bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm (optional)

BUTTONS:
- rounded-xl font-bold shadow-md
- transition-all duration-300
- active:scale-95 (press state)
- disabled: bg-slate-200 text-slate-400 (no shadow)

BADGES:
- text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter
- rounded-full px-md py-xs
- Semantic colors: primary/10, secondary/10, etc.

INPUTS:
- rounded-lg border-2 border-slate-200
- focus:border-primary ring-4 ring-primary/10
- placeholder: italic text-slate-400

EMPTY STATES:
- Use EmptyState component (app/components/empty-state.tsx)
- Consistent across all pages

=== PADDING PATTERNS ===
Card padding: p-lg (1.5rem)
Section padding: px-lg py-2xl (generous vertical)
Gap between items: gap-md (standard)
List spacing: space-y-md

=== RESPONSIVE ===
Mobile: < 640px (single column)
Tablet: 640-1024px (two columns)
Desktop: > 1024px (full layouts)

All use Tailwind breakpoints: sm:, md:, lg:, xl:

=== ACCESSIBILITY ===
- All interactive: min 44x44px
- All links: visible underline or high contrast
- Focus states: outline-primary outline-offset-2
- Motion: respect prefers-reduced-motion
- Color: not sole indicator (use borders + color)

=== DO's & DON'Ts ===
✅ DO use design tokens (p-lg, gap-md, shadow-md-lift)
✅ DO use rounded-[2rem] for hero cards
✅ DO scale hover: scale-1.02, not scale-1.1
✅ DO add transition-all duration-300 to all interactive
✅ DO use EmptyState component (reusable)
✅ DO use border-2 (not border)

❌ DON'T use arbitrary spacing (p-5, gap-3, gap-4)
❌ DON'T use rounded-3xl for vote cards
❌ DON'T forget shadow-md-lift on card hover
❌ DON'T use inline styles
❌ DON'T scale beyond 1.02 (feels janky)
❌ DON'T forget border-2 (border-1 too thin)
